[Civil. No. 766.] JAMES G. JAMES, Appellant, v. GEORGE H. APPEL, Appellee. APPEAL from the District Court of the First Judicial District in and for the County of Pima. Webster Street, Judge. Barnes & Martin, and Selim M. Franklin, Attorneys for Appellant. Hereford & Hazzard, Attorneys for Appellee. January 29, 1902.

Dismissed.

Affirmed. See opinion, 192 U. S. 129; 48 L. Ed. 377.
